Project: Microsoft Stock Price Prediction Using Machine Learning

Description:
A regression-based project to forecast Microsoft stock prices using historical data and machine learning models.

Technologies Used:
Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib, Jupyter Notebook

Features / Highlights:
1.Collected and cleaned historical stock price data.
2.Engineered features to improve model performance.
3.Split dataset into training and testing sets.
4.Implemented regression models: Linear Regression and Random Forest Regressor.
5.Evaluated models using RMSE, MAE, RÂ² score.
6.Visualized predicted vs actual stock prices using line charts.

Outcome:
1.Delivered reliable stock price predictions.
2.Developed an end-to-end predictive workflow.
